  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1001">
<l>vaittāṉvāy cāṉṟa perumporu ḷaḵtuṇṇāṉ </l>
<l>cettāṉ ceyakkiṭanta til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who does not enjoy the immense riches he has heaped up in his house, is (to be reckoned as) dead, (for) there is nothing achieved (by him).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
